社<br />\n<br />\n高中：<br />\n最好搵個全職補習，而比較下d note<br />\n搵個有心教+有實力<br />\n<br />\n私補就要夾人，同睇下你比得起幾多錢<br />\n有時小型補習社，一科收1300,你比多小小，搵一兩個同學一齊補私補，可能更好。"},{"pid":"9d51a67b3cec226860b4dfd4e7041f18e9a327ee","tid":45857,"uid":36789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:51:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote]教IBDP路過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n教ib應該好搵啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote視乎學習能力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以收DSE價錢double."},{"pid":"85bbe290ee955be8942405d81d121aecd44b9fc9","tid":45857,"uid":11897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:58:27.000Z","msg":"其實d補習社都係依d家長取向<br />\nD家長其實都默許人比功課答案比細路抄<br />\nD功課搞掂完就谷佢參加d專攻一科既班或者買d專科練習比佢做<br />\n根本就係本末倒置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}